text: Broadway Through a Keyhole is a 1933 American musical movie directed by Lowell Sherman and starring Constance Cummings, Russ Columbo, Paul Kelly, Blossom Seeley, Gregory Ratoff, Texas Guinan, Abe Lyman. It was distributed by United Artists. == Other websites == * Category:1933 movies Category:1930s musical movies Category:American musical movies Category:Movies directed by Lowell Sherman
